Reared from leaf galls on 
<taxonomicName box="[585,693,1563,1590]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="glauca">
<emphasis box="[585,693,1563,1590]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Q. glauca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sect. 
<taxonomicName box="[765,952,1563,1589]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Cyclobalanopsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[765,952,1563,1589]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Cyclobalanopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Schweger, S. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Tang, C. - T. &amp; Yang, M. - M. &amp; Stone, G. N. &amp; Nicholls, J. A. &amp; Sinclair, F. &amp; Hearn, J. &amp; Bozso, M. &amp; Penzes, Z." box="[974,1223,1563,1590]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 84" refId="ref52592" refString="Schweger, S., Melika, G., Tang, C. - T., Yang, M. - M., Stone, G. N., Nicholls, J. A., Sinclair, F., Hearn, J., Bozso, M. &amp; Penzes, Z. (2015 b) New species of cynipid inquilines of the genus Saphonecrus (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Synergini) from the Eastern Palaearctic, with a re-appraisal of known species world-wide. Zootaxa, 4054 (1), 1 - 84. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4054.1.1" type="journal article" year="2015">
Schwéger 
<emphasis box="[1091,1139,1563,1589]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">et al</emphasis>
. 2015b
</bibRefCitation>
) and undetermined galls on 
<taxonomicName box="[246,359,1599,1626]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="ciliaris">
<emphasis box="[246,359,1599,1626]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Q. ciliaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(sect. 
<taxonomicName box="[433,620,1599,1625]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Cyclobalanopsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[433,620,1599,1625]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">Cyclobalanopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Lobato-Vila, I. &amp; Wang, Y. &amp; Melika, G. &amp; Guo, R. &amp; Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J." box="[644,926,1599,1626]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="1 - 28" refId="ref46786" refString="Lobato-Vila, I., Wang, Y., Melika, G., Guo, R., Xiaoxue, J. &amp; Pujade-Villar, J. (2021 b) A taxonomic review of the gall wasp genus Saphonecrus Dalla-Torre &amp; Kieffer and other oak cynipid inquilines (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae) from mainland China, with updated keys to Eastern Palaearctic and Oriental species. Zoological Studies, 60 (10), 1 - 28. https: // doi. org / 10.6620 / ZS. 2021.60 - 10" type="journal article" year="2021">
Lobato-Vila 
<emphasis box="[788,837,1599,1625]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">et al</emphasis>
